label: Execution context
url: ./execution-context.html
desc:
  - Ensure that "break on exception" is enabled.
  - Load the test case, open Dragonfly and reload the document.
  - Verify that it stops "a.a".
  - Verify that submitting "window" in the console works.
  - Verify that 'window.top == window' returns 'false'.
  - Press continue.
  - Verify that 'window.top == window' returns 'true'.
  - Switch the runtime in the dropdown to the data uri.
  - Verify that 'window.top == window' returns 'false'.
  - Switch back to 'Test execution context'..
  - Verify that 'window.top == window' returns 'true'.

label: Tooltip evaluation context
url: ./multiple-contexts.html
desc:
  - Load the test case, open Dragonfly and reload the document.
  - Select all the different scripts an verify that the tooltip always
    shows the correct value for 'window.foo'.

